# ClamAV

> Open-source anti-virus program
> ClamAV isn't a command, but a set of commands
> More information: https://www.clamav.net

- Show the clip-view page for scan files using the `clamd` daemon:

`clip-view clamdscan`

- Show the clip-view page for scan files without the `clamd` daemon running:

`clip-view clamscan`

- Show the clip-view page for update the virus definitions:

`clip-view freshclam`
